{"tid":1129402,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"朋友比人拎左身份證借左好多錢","createTime":"2019-04-28T12:33:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-28T14:17:17.000Z","uid":244876,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ba2e11ccdb04621f3b7a52255bd8515938c47c17","tid":1129402,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T12:33:51.000Z","msg":"我唔知放邊一版好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n是咁的<br />\n我朋友比佢老公拎左身份證係唔知情下<br />\n借左好多財仔錢，銀行、二三線財仔都有<br />\n<br />\n佢老公話還左某部份錢但係就整假email當證明<br />\n當然冇收到錢<br />\n<br />\n而家就大部份債務去左我朋友到<br />\n我想問<br />\n佢可以點做？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係咪焗住要還曬？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家就諗住逐間借左錢打去/上去<br />\n表示必須有本人簽名先可以借<br />\n先斷左再借錢既機會<br />\n另外就報警<br />\n告盜用他人身份，同虛假文書<br />\n<br />\n執緊證據(whatsapp 對話，email等)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望集大家力量<br />\n同集氣<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d022e98dc8763fde9ffdb008cb3d14259d99efe","tid":1129402,"uid":9942,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T12:34:31.000Z","msg":"你朋友"},{"pid":"9f138290e5a1c6e9fdcdc1ab2f7aa17a8ebed133","tid":1129402,"uid":168730,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T12:34:52.000Z","msg":"憑本事借唔洗還"},{"pid":"1ca56c971cc6b761e555ca89b4aaba2ea5f22cb2","tid":1129402,"uid":209890,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6d022e98dc8763fde9ffdb008cb3d14259d99efe","tid":1129